                            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                                <span class="faq-question-text">42. Can I see product videos or more images?</span>
                                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                            </button>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                                    <p>Yes. Customers can view real product visuals on our TikTok and Instagram pages.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                                <span class="faq-question-text">43. Are the products the same as shown online?</span>
                                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                            </button>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                                    <p>Yes. What you see is what you receive.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                                <span class="faq-question-text">44. Do you edit or enhance product images?</span>
                                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                            </button>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                                    <p>Images may be lightly edited for lighting and clarity, but the product's colour, shape, size, and design are never altered.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                                <span class="faq-question-text">45. Can I request additional photos or videos before ordering?</span>
                                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                            </button>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                                    <p>For selected products, you may contact us via WhatsApp to request additional visuals, subject to availability.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Group 11: Support -->
                <div class="faq-section-group" data-category="support">
                    <h2 class="faq-section-title">Support</h2>
                    <div class="faq-items-container">
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                                <span class="faq-question-text">46. How will I receive order updates?</span>
                                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                            </button>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                                    <p>Order updates are shared via WhatsApp and email throughout the process.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                                <span class="faq-question-text">47. Is customer support available for international customers?</span>
                                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                            </button>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                                    <p>Yes. All customer support is managed from Qatar and is available for both Qatar and Dubai/GCC customers.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                                <span class="faq-question-text">48. What should I do if I need help before placing an order?</span>
                                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                            </button>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                                    <p>Contact our support team via WhatsApp for product details, sizing guidance, service clarification, or to initiate a Personal Shopping request.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- No Results -->
                <div class="faq-no-results" id="faqNoResults" style="display:none;">
                    <h3 class="faq-no-results-title">No results found</h3>
                    <p class="faq-no-results-text">We couldn't find any match for your search. Try checking your spelling or search for another term.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<!-- Bottom Form -->
<section class="contact-form-section">
    <div class="contact-form-inner">
        <div class="contact-form-intro">
            <h2>{{ section.settings.form_heading | default: "Send Us A Message" }}</h2>
            <p>{{ section.settings.form_subheading | default: "Fill out the form and we'll get back to you as quickly as possible." }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-form-wrapper">
            {%- form 'contact', id: 'ContactForm' -%}
                {%- if form.posted_successfully? -%}
                    <div class="wpcf7-response-output sent" role="status">
                        Thanks for contacting us! We'll get back to you as soon as possible.
                    </div>
                {%- elsif form.errors -%}
                    <div class="wpcf7-response-output invalid" role="alert">
                        {{ form.errors | default_errors }}
                    </div>
                {%- endif -%}

                <p>
                    <span>
                        <input type="text" name="contact[first_name]" placeholder="First Name" value="{% if form.first_name %}{{ form.first_name }}{% elsif customer %}{{ customer.first_name }}{% endif %}" required aria-required="true" />
                    </span>
                    <span>
                        <input type="text" name="contact[last_name]" placeholder="Last Name" value="{% if form.last_name %}{{ form.last_name }}{% elsif customer %}{{ customer.last_name }}{% endif %}" required aria-required="true" />
                    </span>
                    <span>
                        <input type="email" name="contact[email]" placeholder="Email" value="{% if form.email %}{{ form.email }}{% elsif customer %}{{ customer.email }}{% endif %}" required aria-required="true" />
                    </span>
                    <span>
                        <input type="tel" name="contact[phone]" placeholder="Phone Number (optional)" value="{% if form.phone %}{{ form.phone }}{% elsif customer %}{{ customer.phone }}{% endif %}" />
                    </span>
                    <span class="full-width">
                        <textarea cols="40" rows="10" name="contact[body]" placeholder="Your Message" required aria-required="true">{% if form.body %}{{ form.body }}{% endif %}</textarea>
                    </span>
                    <input type="hidden" name="contact[customer_type]" value="qatar" id="contact-customer-type" />
                    <input type="submit" class="wpcf7-submit" id="RealContactSubmit" value="Send Message" style="display:none;" />
                </p>
            {%- endform -%}

            <div class="contact-bottom-row">
                <button type="button" class="contact-submit-custom" onclick="document.getElementById('RealContactSubmit').click();">
                    <svg class="contact-submit-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
                        <path d="M17.5 2.5L9.16667 10.8333" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        <path d="M17.5 2.5L12.0833 17.5L9.16667 10.8333L2.5 7.91667L17.5 2.5Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Send a Message</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

